                            <comment id="15266148" author="vsparmar" created="Mon, 2 May 2016 06:08:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Andrey,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I am new to Spark but would like to help on this issue. I have the environment set up in my local system. I have quite recently started going through the code base and am eager to contribute. Can you point me towards the specific module i need to understand to solve this issue?&lt;/p&gt;

